---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About LitRPG Critic"
  description="LitRPG Critic is an independent review and ranking site for LitRPG, progression fantasy, dungeon core, and GameLit books."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">About LitRPG Critic</h1>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        LitRPG Critic is an independent editorial site dedicated to helping readers navigate the fast-growing world of LitRPG,
        progression fantasy, dungeon core, and GameLit fiction.
      </p>
      <p>
        The genre has exploded in recent years, with hundreds of new titles releasing every month across Amazon, Royal Road,
        and Audible. We cut through the noise with honest rankings, sub-genre breakdowns, and regular coverage of new releases.
      </p>
      <h2>Our Data</h2>
      <p>
        Book data — ratings, covers, author information, and genre tags — is sourced from
        <a href="https://litrpgtools.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LitRPGTools.com</a>,
        the largest community database for the genre. We supplement this with our own editorial coverage.
      </p>
      <h2>Amazon Links</h2>
      <p>
        Links to Amazon may be affiliate links. This helps support the site at no extra cost to you.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Have a book recommendation, correction, or inquiry? Visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
